A Beautiful Mind;;93;;74;;PG-13;;A human drama inspired by events in the life of John Forbes Nash Jr., and in part based on the biography "A Beautiful Mind" by Sylvia Nasar. From the heights of notoriety to the depths of depravity, John Forbes Nash Jr. experienced it all. A mathematical genius, he made an astonishing discovery early in his career and stood on the brink of international acclaim. But the handsome and arrogant Nash soon found himself on a painful and harrowing journey of self-discovery.;;Biography,Drama;;Ron Howard;;2001;;Russell Crowe,Ed Harris,Jennifer Connelly,Paul Bettany,Adam Goldberg,Judd Hirsch,Josh Lucas,Anthony Rapp,Christopher Plummer,Austin Pendleton,Jason Gray-Stanford,Vivien Cardone,Stelio Savante;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beautiful_mind